msg":"下面有雙玲會--陳潔玲對賴慰玲,記得投埋佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">最後三輪乙組聯賽賽程:<br />\n<br />\n32.<br />\n<br />\n2018-04-22<br />\n賴慰玲v何雁詩<br />\n陳寶珊v陳潔玲<br />\n歐鎧淳v林映蔚<br />\n蘇麗珊v黃德藍<br />\n勞嘉怡v胡琳<br />\n駱文捷v湯洛雯<br />\n朱智賢v蔡思貝<br />\n周慧敏v菊梓喬<br />\n陳婉婷v王敏奕<br />\n<br />\n33.<br />\n<br />\n2018-05-06<br />\n王敏奕v勞嘉怡<br />\n胡琳v周慧敏<br />\n林映蔚v駱文捷<br />\n蔡思貝v陳寶珊<br />\n陳婉婷v朱智賢<br />\n何雁詩v菊梓喬<br />\n黃德藍v賴慰玲<br />\n陳潔玲v歐鎧淳<br />\n湯洛雯v蘇麗珊<br />\n<br />\n34.<br />\n<br />\n2018-05-13<br />\n賴慰玲v蔡思貝<br />\n朱智賢v陳潔玲<br />\n歐鎧淳v胡琳<br />\n蘇麗珊v林映蔚<br />\n周慧敏v黃德藍<br />\n陳寶珊v王敏奕<br />\n菊梓喬v湯洛雯<br />\n勞嘉怡v陳婉婷<br />\n駱文捷v何雁詩<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"fecc28f6ea96b5814b4839a3e2a6d123ee797539","tid":629434,"uid":92376,"like":46,"dislike":35,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T16:46:00.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2018-4-15 12:46am-10:46pm</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/0yomFrI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0yomFrI.png&h=c2ab17d8&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/zLhocx6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzLhocx6.png&h=2eadf5f6&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(4)陳潔玲v賴慰玲(5)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">聯賽賽時為22小時，會員可於本回覆發起後22小時內於以回覆評分功能(前者上箭咀;後者下箭咀)投選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆評分功能投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">主場女神票數達到15者會按得票相關情況獲得指定額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"1f4c4e452c1f1969be90b2e19b0ea36c29de3ecf","tid":629434,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T16:48:24.000Z","msg":"每場賽事每收到10票,將會捐出$0.1到慈善機構,就算唔夠10票,都會將總票數合併,多出既仙不論多少一律會作新既一毫計算<br />\n<br />\n善款會喺結算後於歇冬期及賽季結束後各捐出一次,希望大家參與同時,仲可以做埋善事,一舉兩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上半季籌到既296元已經捐出,多謝大家支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/518316/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/518316/page/1</a><br />\nclick入上址即可參閱下半季詳盡賽程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/619426/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/619426/page/1</a><br />\nLIHKG香港女神總會盃四強已經抽籤<br />\n文詠珊VS苟芸慧<br />\n李佳芯VS朱千雪<br />\n首回合 4月12日<br />\n次回合 4月18日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/592889/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/592889/page/1</a><br />\nLIHKG環球女神冠軍盃4強已經誕生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地分別係<br />\n新垣結衣(日本)<br />\nIU(韓國)<br />\n謝安琪(香港)<br />\n周子瑜@TWICE(台灣)<br />\n<br />\n抽籤將於下星期舉行,有結果會再另行公佈<br />\n<br />\n希望巴打絲打們到時踴躍參與<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58134fa248e556594edd0d64eb6141073ab151ac","tid":629434,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T16:57:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a50a84de1c68a3d29991caba40da4338daedee","tid":629434,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-14T17:05:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets